title: Media Day recap
itunes:title: Media Day recap
description:
A giant room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Conor Orr -- react to the mad house that was Media Day in Arizona for Super Bowl XLIX. Plus, they discuss the story lines that nobody is talking about but should be!
